'''''Infidel Art''''' is a six-track LP released by the Japanese black metal band [[Sigh (band)|Sigh]]. The songs on this album are longer and more atmospheric than those on Sigh's previous effort, ''[[Scorn Defeat]]''. Five out of the album's six songs reach over eight minute mark.<ref>[http://sigh.gospel-virus.net/infidelart.htm The Slaughtergarden - Infidel Art<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref>

